Subtask 1.2: Install Social Engineering Toolkit
Clone and install SET:

cd /opt
sudo git clone https://github.com/trustedsec/social-engineer-toolkit.git setoolkit
cd setoolkit
sudo pip3 install -r requirements.txt
sudo python3 setup.py install
Subtask 1.3: Configure SET
Create SET configuration directory and run initial setup:

sudo mkdir -p /etc/setoolkit
sudo cp config/set_config /etc/setoolkit/
